# Wazuh Service Names (Use YOUR actual Docker container names!)
# â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
# Find them with: docker ps --format "{{.Names}}" | grep wazuh

# OpenSearch / Wazuh Indexer (Docker service name)
OPENSEARCH_HOST=https://wazuh.indexer:9200
OPENSEARCH_USER=admin
OPENSEARCH_PASS=admin

# Wazuh API (Manager) - Docker service name
WAZUH_API_HOST=https://wazuh.manager
WAZUH_API_PORT=55000
WAZUH_API_USERNAME=wazuh
WAZUH_API_PASSWORD=wazuh

# Wazuh Indexer (Search) - Docker service name
WAZUH_INDEXER_HOST=https://wazuh.indexer
WAZUH_INDEXER_PORT=9200
WAZUH_INDEXER_USERNAME=admin
WAZUH_INDEXER_PASSWORD=admin

# SSL (set to false for self-signed certs)
WAZUH_VERIFY_SSL=false

# OpenAI API Key (for LLM features)
OPENAI_API_KEY=your-openai-api-key-here
